 。一定要提走美金 ，鍾意去日本居住/旅行可以存日元，鍾意去台灣定居/旅行可以兌台幣，如此類推；<br />\n總之唔好乜都唔做， '光復香港'唔係口號！一齊&ldquo;揾香港錢、兌美國金&ldquo;<br />\n再冇其他選擇 香港人不講獨立不分化<br />\n一齊頂硬上！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家記住唔好咁做呀，會影響到香港嘅銀行體系㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:44:58.000Z","msg":"send去狠人度, 如果佢地貼出黎會reach到多d人"},{"pid":"53e85508775e74e08c766be5ff4822a43d6e461f","tid":1684970,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a8cfc1e7d08fa7a15335e3624a4539afbafe6f","tid":1684970,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7754aa5d8bce23b93122e9b1c911a2ae22ae7cba","tid":1684970,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad01f611530c204b3b141e5f2089a797e3693a4","tid":1684970,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dca8892430a355c86953bc0ac2c78d513229846b","tid":1684970,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7768057fbc53bef328dcd3efc328437090bd3c31","tid":1684970,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e9005d1bb52c5218ad6a7184ca327a7ceb35c16","tid":1684970,"uid":325827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:20:34.000Z","msg":"任何涉及錢銀嘅嘢，一定要小心核實可靠性，以免被人騙錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:35:24.000Z","msg":"的確呀，所以要睇實佢哋本數簿，一開始攞少少試下水溫先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"今次呢個捐得過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:59:02.000Z","msg":"我識佢哋啲人，我覺得佢哋都ok嘅，但係你哋驚嘅話，咪少少哋試下先"},{"pid":"8cf0fa79fbc1c124358f6ae1067f7820288e469a","tid":1684970,"uid":277011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"每月有報告，好事"},{"pid":"d1132b63